{"tid":735871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"力抗美貿易關稅政策！中德簽署200億歐元經濟合作協議","createTime":"2018-07-09T23:41:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T01:27:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e4bece999f8e2781e2b9bb9fd9358897b0dcef","tid":735871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:41:08.000Z","msg":"力抗美貿易關稅政策！中德簽署7146億經濟合作協議<br />\n<br />\n2018-07-09<br />\n<br />\n德國總理梅克爾與中國大陸總理李克強9日公開反對美國貿易關稅政策，稱開放的多邊貿易對人人都有利。<br />\n<br />\n在兩國簽署價值200億歐元（約台幣7146.3億元）的經濟合作協議後，李克強稱這顯示國家之間能共同合作。「自由貿易對雙方和世界經濟都起著?有力的主導作用。」<br />\n<br />\n梅克爾則呼籲各國遵守WTO的指導方針，並稱世界「實際上是個多邊相互依存的體系，當我們遵守規則就會有雙贏局面」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3243751\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3243751&d=C10G%2FRT8B9Z%2B5xCVxkotQXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9c027f12\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3243751</a>"},{"pid":"53d6d01c201613cd8446573b5608d12f87a593c4","tid":735871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef143ea1103a29d89cd2ccb41d4cf3ba4351dcc3","tid":735871,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:42:52.000Z","msg":"中美都簽過啦<br />\n簽完照打<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff09a76478a9ed2887c6b0eaa2edbcfeea60dde3","tid":735871,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:43:14.000Z","msg":"侵：美國收你地關稅嘅損失，你地向中國賺返來吧"},{"pid":"2a0cdc6eec794ef6b34520cd3c7ffa50393dadb5","tid":735871,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T23:56:19.000Z","msg":"班歐洲on9"},{"pid":"ab75483dfe5e50bfd52fae0bd7bbf2ca9c697361","tid":735871,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T01:25:40.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"a45758b663027c1ffab0d0ad734779c9e0cc3921","ti